 Eithan Cherem  Unknown 
August 06, 2025 
 To:  Equifax P.O. Box 740256, Atlanta, GA 30374-0256 



To whom it may concern, 
I am formally requesting an investigation into the following account listed on my credit report, as per my rights under the Fair Credit Reporting Act (FCRA). I believe this account has been reported inaccurately or in error. 




Disputed Accounts 


        Account:  CAINE WEINER 
        Account #:  220217*** 
        Reported Status:  Collections 

          "I think this is from some old bill but I never got any notice about it going to collections. I moved apartments around that time so maybe the letters went to the wrong address. I don’t even know if I really owe this amount." I formally dispute this account as inaccurate and unverifiable. Under my rights granted by the Fair Credit Reporting Act (FCRA) sections 609(a) and 611, I demand that you provide copies of any original signed contracts, applications or other documents bearing my signature that you relied upon to report this account. If these documents cannot be produced within 30 days, the account must be deleted from my credit file. Please also provide evidence of assignment or purchase agreements from the original creditor to the collection agency proving legal authority to collect this debt. 













Under section 611 of the FCRA, you are required to respond to this dispute in writing within 30 days. I look forward to your prompt attention to this matter. If the disputed information cannot be verified, I request that it be corrected or removed from my credit report. If you fail to fully verify these accounts with proper documentation within 30 days, I expect them to be deleted immediately as required by law. Failure to comply may result in further legal actions or formal complaints filed with the FTC and CFPB. 
Please respond in writing within 30 days, as required by the Fair Credit Reporting Act (FCRA). 
Thank you for your prompt attention to this matter. 

   To assist with the verification process, I have included a copy of my government-issued photo ID and proof of address.





Sincerely,  Eithan Cherem  
__________________________ Signature 



According to the Fair Credit Reporting Act (FCRA), you are required to complete your investigation within 30 days of receipt of this letter and provide the results in writing. Please confirm all actions taken.





