     Eithan Cherem  Unknown 
    August 06, 2025 
     To:  CITI 
   P.O. Box 6500, Sioux Falls, SD 57117 
    Dear CITI, 



    Dear CITI, I am writing to you regarding my account (Account Number: 518941******) which is currently showing as closed with a history of late payments on my credit report. I understand the importance of maintaining a good credit history and the implications of late payments. I am writing to request a goodwill adjustment due to the circumstances that led to these late payments. 



    In 2022, I experienced a temporary job loss which greatly affected my financial stability. This unfortunate event led to me missing a few payments on my account. Additionally, there were a couple of instances where my bank had issues with the automatic payments. I contacted them immediately and was under the impression that it was resolved. Furthermore, during this period, I moved apartments and I believe some of the notifications regarding my account may have been sent to the wrong address. 



    Since then, I have regained employment and my financial situation has greatly improved. I have been diligent in making my payments on time and have made efforts to catch up on the missed payments. I have also taken steps to ensure that all future notifications regarding my account are sent to my current address. 




    Relevant Account(s) 


         CITI  — Account #: 518941****** — Status: Closed 

          The account with CITI (Account Number: 518941******) is the one in question. It is currently showing as closed with a history of late payments. These late payments were due to a temporary job loss and issues with automatic payments from my bank. However, I have since recovered from these hardships and have made efforts to bring my account up to date. 







    Given these circumstances, I kindly request a goodwill adjustment for the late payments on my account. I believe that these late payments do not accurately reflect my current financial stability and commitment to fulfilling my financial obligations. I appreciate your understanding and consideration in this matter. Thank you for your time and I look forward to your positive response. 





    To assist with the verification process, I have included a copy of my government-issued photo ID and proof of address. 



    Sincerely, 
     Eithan Cherem  
    __________________________ Signature





