   You're in control of your credit journey - every step brings you closer to financial freedom!   Feeling overwhelmed? If any of this feels confusing or too much - you're not alone. We're here to help. Our team can take care of the whole process for you, including mailing the letters - just reach out and ask about our  Done-For-You  service. 

  Your Next Steps 

    Print each letter in this package. 
    Sign every letter with a pen. 
    If a goodwill letter shows "Address not provided — please enter manually," look up the creditor's billing or dispute mailing address online and type it into the PDF. 
    Include a photo ID and recent utility bill. If your dispute is related to identity theft, also include a photo of your Social Security card. 
    Mail via certified mail with tracking. 


  We’ve highlighted below all the actions you should take for each of your credit accounts. 

  Your Final Checklist 

    ☐ Printed all letters 
    ☐ Signed each letter with a pen 
    ☐ Attached a copy of your Photo ID + utility bill 
    ☐ Sent via certified mail with tracking 


